.MARINE...
(Today through Wednesday)
Issued at 351 AM PDT Fri Jun 5 2026

Hazardous conditions for small craft continue through the weekend.
Gale force gusts are expected across the outer waters and along
the  coastal jet regions of Point Reyes and Point Sur today,
expanding to all of the inner waters tomorrow. Very rough seas are
expected in the outer waters with rough seas for the inner waters
through tomorrow. Conditions will slightly begin to improve Sunday
with moderate seas and moderate to fresh northwesterly breezes
expected by Tuesday.

